Concatenation  :- When adding string ( str1 + str2)
Addition :- When adding int + int  or int + float

We can type cast all int and  float values into string
But we cannot typecase all string into integer or float.



Indentation
concentation

###################### Addition + Concatnation Examples ##############################

a = "vlan "
b  = "10"
print (a+b)


c = "nitin"
d = "Vipin"
print(c+" "+d)


##########Typecasting :- like We  can convert string value into interger 

a = int("10")
b = 10

print(a+b)

ping_cmd = "ping" + "8.8.8.8"

######################################################
